                    <h1 class="article__title">SubWhisper Pro vs VEED vs Kapwing 2026: Best AI Subtitle Translation Tool</h1>
                    <div class="article__meta">
                        <span>Published March 13, 2026</span>
                        <span class="article__meta-separator"></span>
