                        </div>

                        <div class="step-block">
                            <div class="step-block__content">
                                <h4>Do these tools work with YouTube videos?</h4>
                                <p>All three tools can generate translated subtitles compatible with YouTube. SubWhisper Pro exports SRT and VTT files that you upload directly to YouTube Studio. VEED can import YouTube URLs directly and burn subtitles into the video. Kapwing also supports YouTube URL imports. For YouTube creators who need translated subtitles in multiple languages, SubWhisper Pro is the most efficient option because of its batch translation capability and lower cost.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

